# khwarizmi-mcp-index.md

### A. Purpose
Master index for all Khwarizmi MCP Rules Files. Defines load order, dependencies, and Syncfusion component library reference for AI tools.

### B. Rule Files and Load Order

| Priority | File | Domain | Mode |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `khwarizmi-design-system.rules.md` | Global + Syncfusion foundation | Always Apply |
| 2 | `vision.rules.md` | Philosophy + AI principles | Always Apply |
| 3 | `tokens.rules.md` | Design tokens (material3) | Always Apply |
| 4 | `colors.rules.md` | Semantic color system | Apply Intelligently |
| 5 | `typography.rules.md` | Type scale + Arabic fonts | Apply Intelligently |
| 6 | `spacing.rules.md` | 8px spatial system | Apply Intelligently |
| 7 | `layouts.rules.md` | 12-column RTL grid | Apply to Specific Files |
| 8 | `components.rules.md` | Syncfusion component mapping | Apply Intelligently |
| 9 | `navigation.rules.md` | SfSidebar, SfAppBar, SfTab | Apply to Specific Files |
| 10 | `forms.rules.md` | FormValidator + Sf inputs | Apply to Specific Files |
| 11 | `tables.rules.md` | SfGrid + SfPivotView | Apply to Specific Files |
| 12 | `feedback.rules.md` | SfToast, SfMessage, SfSkeleton | Apply Intelligently |
| 13 | `patterns.rules.md` | Dashboard, CRUD, Wizard, etc. | Apply Intelligently |

